    {
      "id": "E:note:row442600:1",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "SICU    HPI:    HPI: 69 with h/o gastric PUD s/p antrectomy/Billroth II and then",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row442600#s1",
      "text": "SICU    HPI:    HPI: 69 with h/o gastric PUD s/p antrectomy/Billroth II and then later    Roux-en-Y conversion for reflux problems. [**12-28**] obstructive jaundice    and cholangitis and percutaneous transhepatic cholangio tube was    placed."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row442600:2",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "On imaging there was a mass at the end of the bile duct.",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row442600#s2",
      "text": "On imaging there was a mass at the end of the bile duct."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row442600:3",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "ERCP    showed a cut-off stricture at the ampullary level and MRCP demonstrated ",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row442600#s3",
      "text": "ERCP    showed a cut-off stricture at the ampullary level and MRCP demonstrated    a mass-like effectin the duodenum at that point."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row442600:4",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Pt subsequently    underwent whipple, chole, enteroenterostomy x2 on    [**2173-",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row442600#s4",
      "text": "Pt subsequently    underwent whipple, chole, enteroenterostomy x2 on    [**2173-1-20**]."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row442600:5",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Biopsy revealed adenocarcinoma of dudodenum at the ampulla.",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row442600#s5",
      "text": "Biopsy revealed adenocarcinoma of dudodenum at the ampulla."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row442600:6",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Post-operative course complicated by anastamotic breakdowns of the    hepatojeju",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row442600#s6",
      "text": "Post-operative course complicated by anastamotic breakdowns of the    hepatojejunostomy and pancreaticojejunostomy sites, requiring OR [**2-5**]    for drainage of an intra-abdominal abscess, repair of    pancreaticojejunostomy and subsequent re-drainage and suturing of    intestinal perforations."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row442600:7",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "He has also had IR drainage and drain    placement into a blind ending loop of b",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row442600#s7",
      "text": "He has also had IR drainage and drain    placement into a blind ending loop of bowel leaking into an abdominal    abscess cavity on [**2-12**]."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row442600:8",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "He also had brief dyspnea and persistent hypoxia post-operatively, with    evalu",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row442600#s8",
      "text": "He also had brief dyspnea and persistent hypoxia post-operatively, with    evaluation showing tracheobronchomalacia with bile seen in the trachea."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row442600:9",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "He has had persistent low-grade fevers on broad spectrum antibiotics.",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row442600#s9",
      "text": "He has had persistent low-grade fevers on broad spectrum antibiotics."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row442600:10",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "[**2-20**] he developed a rash in the context of multiple antibiotics for    per",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row442600#s10",
      "text": "[**2-20**] he developed a rash in the context of multiple antibiotics for    persistent fevers."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row442600:11",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "He had eosinophilia of 12% and a slow drop off in    renal function over the pas",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row442600#s11",
      "text": "He had eosinophilia of 12% and a slow drop off in    renal function over the past few weeks."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row442600:12",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "In this setting pt developed    rash c/w reaction to zosyn.",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row442600#s12",
      "text": "In this setting pt developed    rash c/w reaction to zosyn."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row442600:13",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "His renal function worsened, mental status    declined in the setting of uremia,",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row442600#s13",
      "text": "His renal function worsened, mental status    declined in the setting of uremia, pt became hypotensive and    subsequently was transferred to SICU after undergoing hemodialysis."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row442600:14",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "PMH: HTN, ARF ([**2-22**] infectious process),gastric peptic ulcer disease,    A",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row442600#s14",
      "text": "PMH: HTN, ARF ([**2-22**] infectious process),gastric peptic ulcer disease,    Adenocarcinoma of the duodenum, Tracheobronchomalacia, should receive    Fyb-antigen negative products for all red cell transfusions (antibody    may cause hemolytic transfusion reactions)    PSH:    -antrectomy, Billroth II        -Roux-en-Y conversion for reflux    problems    [**Name (NI) **] continues with mild dyspnea today."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row442600:15",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "On 60% Face tent.",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row442600#s15",
      "text": "On 60% Face tent."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row442600:16",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "RR    30-40.",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row442600#s16",
      "text": "RR    30-40."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row442600:17",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "O2 sat has been between 96-98% consistently.",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row442600#s17",
      "text": "O2 sat has been between 96-98% consistently."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row442600:18",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "No signs of    hypoxia evident.",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row442600#s18",
      "text": "No signs of    hypoxia evident."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row442600:19",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Renal failure, acute (Acute renal failure, ARF)    Assessment:    Continues with",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row442600#s19",
      "text": "Renal failure, acute (Acute renal failure, ARF)    Assessment:    Continues with renal failure."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row442600:20",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "BUN/Creat remain elevated.",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row442600#s20",
      "text": "BUN/Creat remain elevated."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row442600:21",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "(72/7.9).",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row442600#s21",
      "text": "(72/7.9)."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row442600:22",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Urine output is labile (15-100 cc s/hr/)    Action:    HD today.  40 mg Lasix gi",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row442600#s22",
      "text": "Urine output is labile (15-100 cc s/hr/)    Action:    HD today.  40 mg Lasix given today as well    Response:    Tolerated HD well, 2L removed.  1 unit RBC s given."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row442600:23",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Plan:    Transfer to the floor.",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row442600#s23",
      "text": "Plan:    Transfer to the floor."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row442600:24",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Continue with HD as ordered.",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row442600#s24",
